quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  36,33,"Hino wonani …ďe maande: leydi yoorundi ndin, Men wuurniti ndi, Men yaltini gabbe e mayri, tawi ko e …óen …ďe √Īaamata"
  36,34,"Men wa…ói e mayri gese tamarooje e inabuuje, Men …ďulni e mayri …ďulli(ceewle)"
  36,35,fii no …ďe √Īaamira dim…óe mun …óen e kon ko …ďe golliri juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen. E …ďe yettataa (Alla)
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii tagu…óo nooneeji …óin On fow: gila e ko leydi ndin fu…óinta kon, haa e wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, e kon ko …ďe anndaa"
  36,37,"Maande goo kadi wonanii …ďe: e jemma on, Me…óen sorta e makko √Īalorma on, tawa …ďe wontii e niwre"
  36,38,"E naange ngen, hinge doga haa e √Īii…ďirde magge; …óum ko e…ď…ďoore Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On"
  36,39,"E lewru ndun, Men e…ď…ďani ndu jipporde, haa ndu wa…ótinira wa baaŇčal tamaro kii…óngal"
  36,40,"Wanaa naange ngen woni ko haanini hewtitagol lewru ndun, wanaa jemma on woni ko aditotoo √Īalorma on; kala majji non, ko e laawol mun woni dogude"
  36,41,"Maande goo wonanii …ďe, wonnde Men roondike geyngol ma…ď…ďe ngol, ka laana hebbinaaka"
  36,42,"Men tagani …ďe sugu makko, ko …ďe wa…ó…óoo"
  36,43,"Si Me…óen yi…óuno, Men yoolayno …ďe; hara faabo alanaa …ďe, wanaa kadi …ďe da…óndetee…ďe"
  36,44,"si wanaa yurmeende immornde e Amen, e dakmitagol haa e saanga"
  36,45,"Si …ďe wi'anaama: \"Rentee e kon ko woni yeeso mon e …ďaawo mon, belajo'o, on yurminte"
  36,46,"Aaya woo e Aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen araali e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa …ďe …óuurnoo…óe"
  36,47,"Si …ďe wi'anaama kadi: \"Wintee(nafqe) e kon Alla arsiki on\", yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'ana gom…óim…ďe …ďen: \"E men √Īamminay on taw…óo si Alla muuyuno, O √Īamminayno mo? On wonaali, si wanaa e nder majjere …ďanngunde"
  36,48,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ďe"
  36,49,"∆Āe habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango wooto, nanngayngo …ďe, hara hi…ďe yeddondira"
  36,50,"∆Āe waawoytaa wasiyagol ontuma, wanaa …ďe ruttoytoo…ďe e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen"